metadata.name: The Hierophant (Kundalini Jesus)
metadata.description:
2020 was one of the most challenging years in human history. 

The world needs hope. 

Jesus was not just a teacher to admire. He also possessed extraordinary abilities. The snake is the symbol of the rising Kundalini reaching the highest chakra. The Enlightenment. 

The Transhumanism idea - people will enter virtual reality and become God-like semi machines merging with Artificial Intelligence. Is this the right path? What if humanity divides into two where a part of people will lead a spiritual path and another one who merges with machines?
